{"tid":2195300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女生藏六角匙索帶被控 兩警作供看不見有人設路障 但指憑裝束打扮相信曾參與堵路","createTime":"2020-09-09T05:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T09:08:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":297,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"caa9b2d1d75f1c013dd5796802bbb171c102680e","tid":2195300,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"去年11月11日網民號召「大三罷」，各處均有示威者阻路事件。21歲女大學生在牛頭角觀塘道遭防暴警追截，搜獲一包袋口密封的六角匙及一包索帶，女生否認一項管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用罪，案件今在觀塘裁判法院開審。兩警作供時均指，現場看不見有人設路障，惟其中一人稱：「根據現場環境裝束及打扮，我相信（她）曾經參與」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/2FNVWXT4QJBTZFBSJZHTGY4B7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2F2FNVWXT4QJBTZFBSJZHTGY4B7Q%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=7f71a7c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2F2FNVWXT4QJBTZFBSJZHTGY4B7Q%2F&h=22b441cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/2FNVWXT4QJBTZFBSJZHTGY4B7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"0729f32ad83b3f7b456b686bab4f4512899375d0","tid":2195300,"uid":183844,"like":220,"dislike":3,"score":217,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:46:43.000Z","msg":"啲狗咁賤<br />\n我相信佢哋食過屎"},{"pid":"b19993e724c5249d5d7e569ab87dcf216a20d89d","tid":2195300,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1dcbc1cb1a9b369aaedcde92a4ac85850abc72c","tid":2195300,"uid":334720,"like":121,"dislike":1,"score":120,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"琴日例子:<br />\n著黑衫戴口罩去戲院 身上乜都無, 都可以話有問題而罪成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0cfa6eb